sentences: Jo Hye-joo (Korean: 조혜주; Hanja: 趙慧珠; born April 18, 1995) is a South Korean actress and model.
She began her acting career with the 2017 film Wedding.
She is best known for her roles in Search: WWW (2019) and the coming of age television series A Love So Beautiful (2020).
